### Get Dashboard Metrics - All Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Dashboard Metrics - Specific Branch
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/metrics?BranchId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Dashboard Metrics - Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/metrics?StartDate=2025-01-01&EndDate=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Dashboard Metrics - Branch and Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/metrics?BranchId=1&StartDate=2025-10-01&EndDate=2025-10-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}